::Hot Rod::

He heard the missile comeing at him. He attempted a back flip, to jump
over it, but he was too slow, and the missile skinned his leg. It wasn't
enough to blow, but it made him drop to the ground, in pain. He crawled
to cover.

OOC: Yanshosh, where the hell are you?! Come back me up, in this
argument, with CODE!
